# 301 redirect: non-trailing-slash → trailing-slash
# Prevents GSC from indexing duplicate URLs (307 → 301 permanent)
/about  /about/  301
/contact  /contact/  301
/privacy-policy  /privacy-policy/  301
/blog  /blog/  301
/blog/:slug  /blog/:slug/  301
/categories  /categories/  301
/categories/:slug  /categories/:slug/  301
